<a href="http://www.mozilla.org" target="_blank">
Mozilla</a> is more than a web browser, it provides a cross-platform framework for 
developing applications.  OEone (now Axentra) produced an operating environment which leveraged
Mozilla to create their Homebase software. The operating environment, Homebase,
contained many components including an 
Address Book, Web Browser, Calendar, Email, File Manger, and Word Processor.  
</P>

